des:
Relaxing Sounds : Singing Bowl & Bird Chirping skill helps you improve memory, focus, and concentration. It helps you sleep peacefully or block out unwanted noise at work or home. You'll be able to sleep better, stay focused, relax quickly and more effectively. 

By default, the sound will play until you stop it. To stop the music, say "Alexa, stop.” To resume it again, say "Alexa, resume."
